('Physion Barcelona', 'Physiotherapy', 'Multilingual physiotherapy and manual therapy clinic founded by Yvonne van Dijk, a highly experienced physiotherapist with over 14 years of clinical experience. Originally from the Netherlands, Yvonne brings expertise in orthopedic injuries, sports rehabilitation, and post-surgical recovery. Services include physiotherapy, manual therapy, personal training, and nutrition coaching. Multilingual services available in English, Dutch, German, and Spanish, catering to expats, students, and international residents. Offers both in-clinic appointments and home visits (additional fee applies). Partnerships with major Barcelona running events including Hyundai Mitja Marató Barcelona and Salomon Run Barcelona. Bachelor''s degree in Physiotherapy from Hanzehogeschool Groningen (2011) and Master of Science in Manual Therapy from SOMT University of Physiotherapy (2019).', 'Passeig de Sant Joan 97, 1-2a', 'Barcelona', 'Barcelona', '+34 627 508 605', 'info@physionbarcelona.com', 'https://physionbarcelona.com/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
